# apps/backend/src/modules/ai/

## Responsibility
AI settings, provider configuration, and playground/session APIs for model routing and experimentation.

## Design
Router + service pattern. Handlers shape API responses while AIService manages settings persistence, provider configs, playground state, personas, and routing strategy.

## Flow
Handlers require resolved app context for app-scoped operations, call AIService for reads/writes/tests, and normalize provider-specific fields into API-friendly responses.

## Integration
Uses Prisma-backed settings/models indirectly through AIService, and integrates with provider backends such as GrowthCircle, Azure, and SumoPod.

